<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Reconciliation Agreement</title>
  <style>
    @page {
      size: a4;
      margin: 0.5in;
    }
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      font-size: 11pt;
      color: #222;
      background: white;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      line-height: 1.4;
    }
    .agreement-header {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }
    .agreement-logo {
      width: 120px;
      height: 60px;
      margin-right: 20px;
    }
    .agreement-title {
      flex: 1;
      text-align: left;
    }
    .agreement-title h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 18pt;
      font-weight: bold;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: #1e3a8a;
    }
    .agreement-summary {
      margin-bottom: 30px;
      background: #f8f9fa;
      border: 1px solid #dee2e6;
      border-radius: 6px;
      padding: 18px 24px;
      font-size: 12pt;
    }
    .summary-row {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    .summary-label {
      font-weight: bold;
      width: 220px;
      color: #333;
    }
    .summary-value {
      flex: 1;
      color: #1e3a8a;
      font-size: 13pt;
    }
    .agreement-section {
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }
    .agreement-section h2 {
      font-size: 13pt;
      color: #1e3a8a;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .agreement-text {
      font-size: 11pt;
      color: #222;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }
    .signature-section {
      display: flex;
      gap: 60px;
      margin-top: 40px;
    }
    .signature-box {
      border: 1px solid #999;
      border-radius: 6px;
      padding: 24px 18px;
      min-width: 260px;
      text-align: center;
      background: #f8f9fa;
    }
    .signature-line {
      border-bottom: 1px solid #222;
      margin: 24px 0 8px 0;
      min-height: 28px;
    }
    .signature-label {
      font-size: 10pt;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #333;
    }
    .agreement-footer {
      margin-top: 40px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 9pt;
      color: #666;
      border-top: 1px solid #ccc;
      padding-top: 12px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="agreement-header">
    <% if (flDmsLogo) { %>
      <img src="<%= flDmsLogo %>" alt="FL-DMS Logo" class="agreement-logo" />
    <% } %>
    <div class="agreement-title">
      <h1>Reconciliation Agreement</h1>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="agreement-summary">
    <div class="summary-row">
      <div class="summary-label">State Name:</div>
      <div class="summary-value"><%= stateName %></div>
    </div>
    <div class="summary-row">
      <div class="summary-label">Monthly SASP Net Fees in Pennies:</div>
      <div class="summary-value"><%= monthlySaspNetFees %></div>
    </div>
    <div class="summary-row">
      <div class="summary-label">Monthly American Surplus Net Fees in Pennies:</div>
      <div class="summary-value"><%= monthlyAmericanSurplusNetFees %></div>
    </div>
    <div class="summary-row">
      <div class="summary-label">Total Monthly Fees in Pennies:</div>
      <div class="summary-value"><%= totalMonthlyFees %></div>
    </div>
    <div class="summary-row">
      <div class="summary-label">Report Period:</div>
      <div class="summary-value"><%= reportPeriod %></div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="agreement-section">
    <h2>Agreement Statement</h2>
    <div class="agreement-text">
      By signing below, each party hereto certifies that an authorized representative has reviewed the Reconciliation Report for the Report Period set forth above and hereby accepts the account reconciliation for that period, including the amounts due and payable to each party hereto. Each signatory represents and warrants they have authority to bind their respective parties hereto. This acceptance authorizes settlement/disbursement in accordance with any underlying agreements between the parties and this Reconciliation Statement for the applicable Report Period. Acceptance is limited to the Report Period and does not waive either Party’s audit, verification, or other contractual rights. Electronic signatures and counterparts are valid and enforceable.
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="signature-section">
    <div class="signature-box">
      <div class="signature-line"></div>
      <div class="signature-label">State Administrator Signature</div>
    </div>
    <div class="signature-box">
      <div class="signature-line"></div>
      <div class="signature-label">American Surplus Administrator Signature</div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="agreement-footer">
    <div>Agreement File: <%= agreementFileName %></div>
    <div>Generated by American Surplus Platform</div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
